### Register a new user
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "reception-{{$uuid}}",
  "email": "reception-{{$uuid}}@example.com",
  "password": "Passw0rd!",
  "role": "RECEPTION",
  "phone": "0712345678",
  "city": "Cluj-Napoca"
}

> {%
    client.global.set("registeredEmail", response.body.email);
%}

###

### Register with a duplicate email -> 409 Conflict
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "someone-else",
  "email": "{{registeredEmail}}",
  "password": "Passw0rd!",
  "role": "RECEPTION"
}

###

### Login -> access token + refresh token
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "{{registeredEmail}}",
  "password": "Passw0rd!"
}

> {%
    client.global.set("accessToken", response.body.accessToken);
    client.global.set("refreshToken", response.body.refreshToken);
%}

###

### Login with wrong password -> 401
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "{{registeredEmail}}",
  "password": "wrong-password"
}

###

### GET /api/auth/me without a token -> 401
GET http://localhost:8080/api/auth/me

###

### GET /api/auth/me with the access token
GET http://localhost:8080/api/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### Any protected Module 1 endpoint without a token -> 401
GET http://localhost:8080/api/rooms

###

### The same endpoint with the access token -> works
GET http://localhost:8080/api/rooms
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### Refresh the access token using the refresh token
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/refresh
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refreshToken": "{{refreshToken}}"
}

> {%
    client.global.set("accessToken", response.body.accessToken);
    client.global.set("refreshToken", response.body.refreshToken);
%}

###

### Logout (revokes all refresh tokens for this user)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/logout
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### Using the now-revoked refresh token -> 401
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/refresh
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refreshToken": "{{refreshToken}}"
}
